reviewText: Love this movie. Love the price. But skips all the time since day one sad to say looking to have to buy another one one again

If you are a fan of dancing movies such as Fame, Step Up movies, and the Center Stage movies you will likely enjoy this movie. It is not the best dancing movie I've ever seen but I did like it for the moves and music. Otherwise it's not my favorite.
Terrible, just terrible...  About as predictable as a washing machine.  Actually!  A washing machine would be more fun to watch...  Fact!
